<https://www.gov.uk/government/people/pat-mcfadden> <http://ogp.me/ns#title> "The Rt Hon Pat McFadden MP"@en .
<https://www.gov.uk/government/people/pat-mcfadden> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "Pat McFadden was appointed Secretary of State for Work and Pensions on 5 September 2025. He was previously Chancellor of the Duchy of Lancaster between 5 July 2024 and 5 September 2025 and Minister for Intergovernmental Relations between 5 September 2024 and 6 September 2025. He was elected as the MP for Wolverhampton South East in May 2005."@en .
